hdfs-fdw (2.3.3-1PIGSTY) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial package for hdfs_fdw 2.3.3.
  * Build version-specific packages for PostgreSQL 14 through 18.
  * Keep the private libhive bridge co-located with an origin rpath.
  * Verify source integrity and generate automatic debug symbols.
  * Build Java 8-compatible bytecode, use the Debian Java share directory, and
    apply full linker hardening to the private bridge.

